title: Child Stuck Between Walls and Rescue Operation
description: A toddler is wedged between two closely set walls, visibly distressed. A man is attempting to reach and rescue the child. The back of the photograph contains typed and stamped information indicating a rescue operation in San Francisco, involving police and firefighters responding to a distress call.
